node.text: @grossypelosi is back with another family recipe, this time with an extra special guest! Today, he’s sharing the recipe for his grandfather Bimpy’s Giambotta (Italian vegetable stew), which is a celebration of the bountiful garden harvest that signals the end of summer. Get the recipe at the link in bio. #f52community

node.title: Bimpy's Giambotta with Dan Pelosi - At Home With Us

node.text: Weekend plans, we got 'em: Fire up the grill and make this garlicky, citrusy chicken + crispy potatoes from @acozykitchen. Pour a glass of your fave @imagerywinery wine to go with, and dinner's all set. Leftovers? Yep, we've got ideas for those too. Click the link in bio to snag the recipe while summer's still here. #f52partner

node.title: 2 Food and Wine Pairings for Summer with @acozykitchen

node.text: Resident @amychaplin's vegetable dressings are the key to transform everyday meals into something special instantly. node.text: Inspired by the food covers many Asian cultures have been using for generations, this handmade collapsible woven food tent is another #f52bestof that our community could not get enough of. This version is crafted by expert weavers in the Philippines, so each purchase helps support the basketry cottage industry (you bet it's fair trade). Click on the link in our bio to get yours. 📸: @jamesransom_nyc
